# CODEOWNERS for Interakt
# ------------------------------------------------------------------
# This file defines who is automatically requested for review on PRs.
# Combined with the "require_code_owner_review" rule on main,
# it ensures no PR merges without a maintainer's approval.
#
# Rules:
#   - Owners must have WRITE access to the repo (teams must be granted access).
#   - The LAST matching pattern wins, so keep the broad "*" line at the top
#     and put more specific paths below it.
#
# ------------------------------------------------------------------

# Default owner for everything not matched by a more specific rule below.
# Use a maintainers TEAM if you have one, otherwise your personal handle.
*                       @alphasolutionsrepo/interakt-maintainers

# CI, automation, and repo config — keep tightly held.
/.github/               @alphasolutionsrepo/interakt-maintainers
/.github/workflows/     @alphasolutionsrepo/interakt-maintainers
/.github/CODEOWNERS     @alphasolutionsrepo/interakt-maintainers
